@startuml
title SomeTrails Route Editor

actor User
participant "SomeTrails" as ST
participant "Trail Editor" as TE
participant "Snap/Draw" as SDM
participant "Uploader" as UP
participant "Waypoints" as POI

participant "Route Info Preview" as RPI
participant "Route Preview" as RP
participant "Exporter" as E
participant "Route Submission" as SNR

== Creating a Trail - Auth Required ==

User -> ST : Navigate to Explore Dropdown
ST --> TE : Switch to Trail Editor
User -> TE : Select Mode
TE --> SDM : Mode Switch/Interact
SDM --> TE : Reflect Changes
TE --> UP : Mode Upload
UP --> TE : Reflect Changes
TE --> POI : Mode Add Waypoints
POI --> TE : Reflect Changes

== Save/Publish ==

User -> TE : Accessing Existing Editor Instance
TE -> RPI : User clicked "Save"
RPI --> RP : User clicked "Preview Route"
RPI --> E : Export GPX/TCX format
RPI --> SNR : Formally suggest new trail

@enduml
